{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_11043.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story09","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101201,"motion":1,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"御园花凛","textCenter":"今天也做了件好事！","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101201}],"textCenter":"[chara:101201:effect_emotion_joy_0][se:7222_happy]甚至不输给魔法希凛呢！"},{"nameRight":"？？？","textRight":"那个，@能打扰一下吗？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101201,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"御园花凛","nameRight":"八千代","textCenter":"找我有事吗？"},{"autoTurnLast":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100201,"motion":201,"pos":2},{"id":101201,"pos":0}]},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101201,"lipSynch":0,"pos":0}],"textLeft":"（是七海八千代……）"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story08","chara":[{"id":100201}],"textRight":"我在找一个人。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101201,"motion":1}],"textLeft":"好、好的……"},{"chara":[{"id":100201,"motion":1}],"textRight":"年纪跟你差不多。"},{"chara":[{"id":100201}],"textRight":"身高跟你差不多。"},{"chara":[{"id":100201}],"textRight":"长得跟你差不多。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100201,"motion":100}],"textRight":"头发颜色也跟你差不多，@你认识这样的人吗？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101201,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"诶……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_042.exp.json","id":100201,"motion":0}],"textRight":"你肯定认识吧？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100201,"motion":0}],"textRight":"毕竟我要找的就是你啊，@怪盗花凛。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"effect":"ef_adv_05","face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100200,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"se":"7205_magic_girl","textRight":"好了，@把悲叹之种还给我。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"effect":"ef_adv_05","face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":101200,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"se":"7205_magic_girl","textLeft":"办、办不到！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_042.exp.json","id":100200}],"textRight":"你果然是怪盗花凛。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_022.exp.json","id":101200}],"textLeft":"我没有悲叹之种！@已经不在我身上了！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":100200,"motion":0}],"textRight":"难道说……你用掉了？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101200,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"我给别人了……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_042.exp.json","id":100200}],"textRight":"给人了？为什么？"},{"chara":[{"id":101200}],"textLeft":"为了帮助魔法少女……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100200,"motion":1}],"textRight":"呼，是吗。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100200}],"textRight":"你还真是诚实啊。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"effect":"ef_adv_05","face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100201,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"se":"7205_magic_girl","textRight":"这样一来，我似乎就不用@特地教训你了。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101200,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"教训我？"},{"chara":[{"id":100201}],"textRight":"对。我原本是想听听你的回答，@然后决定要不要认真和你打一场。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100201,"motion":201}],"textRight":"现在看来，@口头上说说你就足够了。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":101200}],"textLeft":"这、这是什么意思……"},{"chara":[{"id":100201}],"textRight":"其实，那个悲叹之种@是我故意让你偷去的。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_042.exp.json","id":100201,"motion":200}],"textRight":"然后监视你会怎么使用它。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101200}],"textLeft":"你就早知道了……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100201}],"textRight":"没错，我听说过你的传闻。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100201,"motion":0}],"textRight":"然后今天，@我亲眼见识到了。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100201,"motion":100}],"textRight":"所以容我说一句。"},{"chara":[{"id":100201,"motion":200}],"textRight":"今后不要再做这种蠢事了。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":101200,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"但我必须帮助那些弱者。"},{"chara":[{"id":101200,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"为了那些@无法与魔女作战的女孩子……"},{"chara":[{"id":101200}],"textLeft":"我要把悲叹之种分给她们。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100201,"motion":0}],"textRight":"既然如此，那请你自己去狩猎魔女，@然后将悲叹之种分给她们。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_052.exp.json","id":101200,"lipSynch":0,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"——！？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_042.exp.json","id":100201}],"textRight":"就算是强大的魔法少女，@也会消耗魔力，陷入危机。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100201,"motion":1}],"textRight":"在你偷走悲叹之种之时……"},{"chara":[{"id":100201}],"textRight":"如果那个人的魔力@已经濒临极限了怎么办？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101200,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"那个……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100201,"motion":200}],"textRight":"若是运气不好，她们或许就会@因为你的缘故被魔女杀掉。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101200,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"怎、怎么会……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101200}],"textLeft":"但她们很强……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100201}],"textRight":"和强不强无关。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100201,"motion":300}],"textRight":"盗取悲叹之种，@和盗取金钱是不一样的……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100201,"motion":0}],"textRight":"怪盗花凛……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100201,"motion":201}],"textRight":"你啊，@一直在间接地杀害魔法少女哦。"},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_052.exp.json","id":101200}],"textLeft":"诶……"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story12","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":101200,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"不是的，不是这样的！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100201,"motion":0}],"textRight":"既然觉得不是这样，@那你就不要再依赖别人了。"},{"chara":[{"id":100201}],"textRight":"通过自己的努力，@把东西分给别人。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100201,"motion":100}],"textRight":"你的志向@倒是可取的……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101200,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"…………"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100201,"motion":0}],"textRight":"我想说的就是这些。"},{"nameNarration":"御园花凛","narration":"怪盗花凛是@弱小魔法少女的伙伴……","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"可是，我却因此……@害死了强大的魔法少女"},{"narration":"是这样吗？"},{"narration":"我是个，坏人？"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_022.exp.json","id":101201,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1012_00_03","textHome":"陷入危机的魔法花凛……结局会如何！的说…"}],"nameCenter":"御园花凛","textCenter":"危险的魔法花凛……@最后的结局会如何呢！","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":101201}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":101201,"motion":0}]},{"chara":[{"id":101201}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}